mdbtoolr licensing
==================

This package bundles source code from the upstream mdbtools project under
`src/mdbtools/`.

Upstream license files included in this package:
- `src/mdbtools/COPYING`: GNU General Public License, version 2 (GPL-2)
- `src/mdbtools/COPYING.LIB`: GNU Library General Public License, version 2
  (LGPL-2)

The mdbtoolr package metadata therefore declares:
- `License: GPL-2 | LGPL-2`

The complete license texts are provided in the upstream files listed above.
